00:20:11.127 --> 00:20:12.800
<i>Abbey Road by The Beatles.</i>

203
00:20:12.920 --> 00:20:14.868
<i>You would always see
Bridge Over Troubled Water</i>

204
00:20:14.964 --> 00:20:16.511
by Simon and Garfunkel.

205
00:20:16.607 --> 00:20:19.135
<i>And you would always see
Cold Fact by Rodriguez.</i>

206
00:20:19.260 --> 00:20:22.309
To us. it was one of the most
